HEADWORD: Subvention
<hw>Sub*ven"tion</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To subventionize.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subventionize</ent>⟦br⟧
